UMLAZI A manhunt is under way after a mass shooting in Umlazi, KwaZulu-Natal.The assailants opened fire on people having drinks at a local shebeen on Friday night and then moved to a nearby house where they shot at family members and raped a girl.Four people were killed and eight others wounded. This little boy was being breastfed when his mother was shot in the head. #UmlaziMassacre pic.twitter.com/sCzIhBc6d8 A survivor said he thought one of the suspects looked familiar.eNCA